{
  "description": "A nighttime long exposure photograph showcases a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and a bridge. The fireworks are a brilliant white and gold, bursting in the upper center of the frame. Below, a long bridge with illuminated lights stretches across dark water, connecting to a city skyline composed of illuminated buildings. The cityscape is densely packed with structures, with taller buildings prominently featuring in the center. The water reflects some of the city lights, creating shimmering trails.  The overall scene evokes a sense of celebration and urban beauty. There are navigational lights visible on the water, indicating boat traffic.",
